      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EIDETIC MEMORY (2) produced an impressive win last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 3.5 lengths (20.47) at this track. Good beginner and aided by a handy draw. The one to beat again. BEAUTY MARK (8) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 20.79 beating Hello Cindy Lou. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. TOMMY TANGLES (1) turned in a moderate performance last time when sixth at this track over 520m behind Zipping Smee (30.28) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Shapes as one to consider. FRENCH REVOLVER (7) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
